title: Combine press conferences reaction
itunes:title: Combine press conferences reaction
description:
A room with some heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal and Chris Wesseling -- are joined by NFL Now host Colleen Wolfe to discuss the latest news including RGIII's appointment as the starter in Washington, Larry Fitzgerald's new contract and much more. Then Marc Sessler, Kevin Patra, Conor Orr and Dan Hanzus call in from Indianapolis with reactions to the NFL Combine coach press conferences.
